<html>
	<head>
		<title>Email | Account Update</title>
	</head>
	<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
	
	<table width="100%" border="0" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#ffffff">
		<tr style="height:50px;">
			<td>&emsp;</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td align="center" valign="top">
				<table width="900" border="6" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" bordercolor="#CED8F6">
					<tr>
						<td align="center" valign="top" bgcolor="#ffffff">
							<table width="850" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
								<tr style="height:30px;">
									<td valign="middle">&nbsp;</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td align="left" valign="top">
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Hi #if ($ctx.isFirstName) ${firstName}#end,</font></p>
									
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Thank you for your order! </font></p>
										
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">We will send you another email once the items in your order have been shipped.</font></p>
										
										<p><font color="#11309F" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Meanwhile, you can check the status of your order on tatamall.com </b></font></p>
										<p><font color="#11309F" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Please find below the summary of your order with reference number :($ctx.orderCode) </b></font></p>
										
										<p>
											<table width="100%">
												#foreach( $childorder in ${ctx.childOrders} )
												<tr>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Order Number</b></font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>${childorder.code}</b></font></td>
												</tr>
												#foreach($entry in ${childorder.childEntries})
												<tr>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Sr.No</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Transaction ID</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Name Of Product</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Qty</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Price</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Shipping Charge if any</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">COD charges if any</font></td>
												</tr>
												<tr>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.entryNumber</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.orderLineId</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.product.name</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.quantity</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.product.priceQuantity</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">$entry.deliveryAddress</font></td>
													<td><font color="#000" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"></font></td>
												</tr>
												#end
												#end
											</table>
										</p>
										
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
										
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
										
										<p>	<span>Total=INR</span><span>${ctx.totalPrice}</span><span>with INR</span><span>${ctx.shippingCharge}</span><span>Shipping Charge</span></p>
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Please note that the Order Reference Number uniquely identifies your order and the order number uniquely identifies each sub- order at a seller level. Quoting Order Reference Number or order number in communications with us, will help us serve you faster.</font></p>
										<p>&nbsp;</p>
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Delivery details are as follows:</font></p>
                                        									
										<p>Name of person-not yet done</p>
										<p>${ctx.deliveryAddress}</p>
										<p>Mobile Number of person-not yet done</p>
										<p>Please note that you have chosen to receive SMS alerts on order status on your number</p>
										<p>{$ctx.mobilenumber}</p>
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Yours Truly,</font></p>
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Tata Mall Team</font></p>	
										<p>
											<table width="40%">
												<tr><td>---------------------------------------------------</td></tr>
												<tr><td><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Tata Mall.... The Joy of Shopping</font></td></tr>
												<tr>
													<td>
														<font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
															<a href="mailto:www.tatamall.com" style="color: #11309F;">www.tatamall.com</a>
														</font>
													</td>
												</tr>
												<tr><td>---------------------------------------------------</td></tr>
											</table>
										</p>
										
										<p><font color="#000" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">&nbsp;</font></p>
										
										<p><font color="#848484" size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">
											This email can't receive replies. For more information, visit Tata Mall's 
											<a href="mailto:talktous@mpl.com" style="color: #11309F;">talktous@mpl.com</a> or write to us at
											<a href="mailto:support@tatamall.com" style="color: #11309F;">support@tatamall.com</a>.
										</font></p>
									</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>	
									<td>&nbsp;</td>
								</tr>
								<tr>
									<td>&nbsp;</td>
								</tr>
							</table>
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td>&nbsp;</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>
</html>

